---
<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 via-pink-500 to-orange-400 text-white py-24 md:py-36"
>
  <!-- Effets décoratifs -->
  <div
    class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-3xl"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/3 -right-32 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-3xl"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <!-- Logo -->
      <div class="mb-10 flex justify-center">
        <img
          src="/images/clubs/Logo-Inter-Asso.webp"
          alt="Logo Inter-Asso IUT Lannion"
          class="h-28 w-28 md:h-36 md:w-36 drop-shadow-xl animate-fade-in"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Titre -->
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6 leading-tight tracking-tight"
      >
        L’Inter-Asso de l’IUT de Lannion
      </h1>

      <!-- Sous-titre -->
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-6 text-white/90 font-medium">
        Le cœur de la vie étudiante
      </p>

      <!-- Description -->
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-12 text-white/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Clubs, événements, partenariats et initiatives étudiantes : l’Inter-Asso
        rassemble, dynamise et fait vivre la communauté de l’IUT de Lannion.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/clubs"
          class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-purple-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:bg-gray-100"
        >
          Découvrir les clubs
          <span class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1">→</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="/evenements"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl border-2 border-white/80 px-8 py-4 font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:bg-white hover:text-purple-600"
        >
          Voir les événements
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Vague bas de section -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
    <svg
      viewBox="0 0 1440 120"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      class="w-full"
    >
      <path
        d="M0 96L80 90C160 84 320 72 480 70C640 68 800 76 960 82C1120 88 1280 92 1360 94L1440 96V120H0V96Z"
        fill="white"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
